headline: Scholastic (SCHL) Lags Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Scholastic (SCHL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -20.87% and 1.69%, respectively, for the quarter ended November 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
